HEADWORD: percent
<hw>per*cent"</hw> <pr>(p⟦etil⟧r*s⟦ecr⟧nt")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
proportion multiplied by 100; <as>as, he receives a <ex>percent</ex> of
the proceeds; 3 is 75 <ex>percent</ex> of 4</as>. Often symbolized by
the character ⟦ldquo⟧%⟦rdquo⟧; <as>as, at 6% interest</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> percentage, per cent, pct.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Percentage</ent>⟦br⟧
